713838f-a.title: Manhattan: 57th Street - 2nd Avenue
713838f-a.text:
57th Street, north side, east fromm Second Avenue, taken from 57th
Street station of the Second Avenue Elevated. In the centre may
be seen the demolition of No. 313 East 57th Street to permit the
construction of the approach to the upper level of the Queens-
borough Bridgc.
September 2, 1928.
P. L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.

713833f-a.title: Manhattan: 57th Street (East) - 2nd Avenue
713833f-a.text:
Clearing for the construction of the upper level of the Queens-
borough Bridge, 313 East 57th Street, north side, east of Second
Avenue.
October 21, 1930.
P. L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.
